###

### Create order with single item
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_num": "555-1234",
  "user_id": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Create order with multiple items
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_num": "555-5678",
  "user_id": 2,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": 1,
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "item_id": 4,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "item_id": 7,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### Test error: Order with no items (should fail)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_num": "555-9999",
  "user_id": 3,
  "items": []
}

###

### Test error: Order with non-existent item (should fail)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_num": "555-8888",
  "user_id": 3,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": 999,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

